PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (PRD)
1. Product Overview

Product Name (Working Title):
InteriorPro – Interior Design & Renovation Estimator

Product Type:
Web Application (Responsive, Mobile-First)

Primary Objective:
Enable users to estimate the cost of a full interior makeover—including residential, commercial, office, and furniture work—by selecting predefined packages and customization options.

Core Value Proposition:

Transparent pricing

Quick cost estimation

Structured packages (Basic, Standard, Premium)

Covers new interiors + renovation projects

2. Target Users
2.1 Primary Users

Homeowners (Flats, Villas, Independent Houses)

Office Owners / Startups

Commercial Space Owners (Shops, Cafes, Showrooms)

2.2 Secondary Users

Interior Design Firms

Contractors

Sales Teams (for quotations)

3. User Personas
Persona 1: Residential Owner

Wants full home interior within a fixed budget

Needs quick cost estimate before meeting designer

Persona 2: Commercial Owner

Wants office/store interior with furniture & lighting

Requires renovation + modular furniture pricing

Persona 3: Sales Executive

Uses app to generate quotation for clients

